============================================
CONVEX
============================================
Your Convex deployment client URL
Found in: Convex Dashboard → Settings → URL & Deploy Key
Starts with: https://your-deployment.convex.cloud
NEXT_PUBLIC_CONVEX_URL=
Your Convex production deploy key (NEVER prefix with NEXT_PUBLIC)
Found in: Convex Dashboard → Settings → URL & Deploy Key
→ Generate Production Deploy Key
Used by: Vercel build command to deploy functions
CONVEX_DEPLOY_KEY=
Your Convex HTTP actions URL (different from above)
Found in: Convex Dashboard → Settings → URL & Deploy Key → HTTP Actions URL
Starts with: https://your-deployment.convex.site
Used by: Clerk webhook endpoint URL
NEXT_PUBLIC_CONVEX_SITE_URL=
============================================
CLERK AUTH + BILLING
============================================
Found in: Clerk Dashboard → API Keys → Publishable key
Starts with: pk_test_ (dev) or pk_live_ (prod)
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=
Found in: Clerk Dashboard → API Keys → Secret keys
Starts with: sk_test_ (dev) or sk_live_ (prod)
NEVER prefix with NEXT_PUBLIC
CLERK_SECRET_KEY=
Found in: Clerk Dashboard → Webhooks → your endpoint → Signing Secret
Starts with: whsec_
Only exists after you create the webhook endpoint in Clerk
CLERK_WEBHOOK_SECRET=
These control where Clerk redirects users
Do not change these unless you change your route structure
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_IN_URL=/sign-in
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_UP_URL=/sign-up
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_AFTER_SIGN_IN_URL=/dashboard
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_AFTER_SIGN_UP_URL=/dashboard
============================================
RESEND (EMAIL)
============================================
Found in: resend.com → API Keys → Create API Key
Starts with: re_
RESEND_API_KEY=
============================================
ANTHROPIC (CLAUDE API)
============================================
Found in: console.anthropic.com → API Keys → Create Key
Starts with: sk-ant-
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
============================================
UPSTASH REDIS (RATE LIMITING)
============================================
Found in: console.upstash.com → your database → REST API
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
Found in: console.upstash.com → your database → REST API
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=
============================================
SENTRY (ERROR MONITORING)
============================================
Found in: sentry.io → your project → Settings → Client Keys
Starts with: https://
SENTRY_DSN=
Found in: sentry.io → Settings → Auth Tokens
SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN=
Found in: sentry.io → Settings → General → Organization Slug
SENTRY_ORG=
Found in: sentry.io → your project → Settings → General → Name
SENTRY_PROJECT=
============================================
APP CONFIGURATION
============================================
Local development URL — do not change this
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000
Your production URL — change before deploying
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://sitefix.com
Your app display name
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_NAME=SiteFix
Comma-separated list of Clerk user IDs with admin access
Found in: Clerk Dashboard → Users → click your user → User ID
Starts with: user_
Example: user_abc123,user_def456
ADMIN_USER_IDS=
